headline.main: U.S. Top Court Rejects Ex-UBS Trader's Challenge to Libor Indictment
headline.print_headline: U.S. Top Court Rejects Ex-UBS Trader's Challenge to Libor Indictment

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Supreme Court on Monday rejected a bid by a former trader with Swiss global financial services company UBS AG to dismiss a criminal indictment filed by U.S. prosecutors over his alleged role in Libor benchmark interest rate manipulation.
